                    {
                        "text": "Approved by: Antimicrobial committee Authorised by: Medicines Optimisation Committee (SUH) Medicines Management Committee (BTUH) Medicines Optimisation & Safety Group (MEH) Joint Document Management Group \u2013 01/12/2020"
